graph LR
    subgraph "Planning Phase"
        Goal[User Goal]
        Embedding[Sentence Transformer]
        VectorSearch[ChromaDB Vector Search]
        Memory[(Past Experiences)]
        Context[Context Builder]
        LLM[Gemini LLM]
    end

    Goal --> Embedding
    Embedding --> VectorSearch
    VectorSearch --> Memory
    Memory --> Context
    Context --> LLM
    LLM --> Plan[Execution Plan]

    Plan -.->|Success| Memory